description:
Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

Download the Neste App with new features!


Pay for refueling, charging your electric vehicle, car wash and Easy Fill windshield wash liquids with the Neste App – using Visa card no longer requires strong authentication. You can now also subscribe to Easy Wash service for unlimited car washes at a selected station for a monthly fee! You can pay in the app with a debit/credit card, Neste Private card, Neste Corporate card or with Apple Pay. Add your Plussa card as a benefit card to receive valuable benefits (not applicable with the Neste Corporate card). Neste App also works in Estonia, Latvia and Lithuania (Easy Wash subscription not available in these countries).

Remember to enable push messages to receive valuable, personalised benefits and discounts!

With Neste App you can


•	Pay for refueling, charging your electric vehicle, and car washes on Neste stations
•	Subscribe to unlimited car washes on selected Easy Wash station for a fixed monthly fee
•	Fill your windshield wash liquids with Easy Fill
•	Find Neste stations and their offers and benefits
•	Monitor your fuel consumption and emissions


If you are a lease car driver at LeasePlan, Arval or Fleet Innovation, contact your leasing company to activate your corporate payment.

The K Charge app makes charging your electric or hybrid vehicle easy, and provides access to the entire Finland-wide charging network for electric vehicles.

Using the app you will, among other things:
•	Be able to find all stations in the K Charge network on the map, and to navigate to the stations
•	See the free and occupied charging points at each station
•	Start and finish each charging session without having to separately process the payment for the charge. 
•	Order a K Charge tag using which you can start and finish each charging session without having to separately process the payment for the charge
•	Monitor the status of the charge (the price in € and the charge in kWh)
•	Monitor your charging history on a monthly basis
•	Collect Plussa points for the charging.

Plugit APP is a completely renewed charging application that lets you easily find the nearest charging point and start and stop charging.

The application provides extensive information about your charging events with new features and improved usability. In addition to the charged energy, duration, and price, you can look at, for example, the amount of carbon dioxide emissions reduced when driving an EV instead of a petrol car.

With the application, you can also manage your RFID-tags and you can, among other things, disable the roaming feature.

Plugit APP replaces the old Plugit Cloud charging application. Your user account and information are automatically transferred to the new application.

Autopay - Park & Charge is your ultimate solution for seamless parking and EV charging. By revolutionising the parking industry through digitisation, we eliminate the hassles and inconveniences from your parking experience. Our customer-friendly app, powered by automatic licence plate recognition, ensures a smooth and hassle-free experience for all users!

Based in Oslo, Norway, Autopay Technologies AS is a software company dedicated to creating the world's best parking management system. We strive to redefine how parking and charging are managed, in order to be more customer-friendly!

Autopay - Park & Charge:
- Pay for parking and EV charging, directly from your phone.
- Easy and quick profile registration.
- Easy management of your vehicles, allowing you to add and edit your information.
- Add two different payment cards for added flexibility.
- Pay only for the duration of your charging session, with the freedom to stop charging while continuing to park.
- Map displaying all Autopay parking and charging spots
- See your agreements and customer clubs
- Find and download receipts effortlessly.
- Search and pay for vehicles retrospectively.

With Autopay, you can enjoy our services in major cities such as Oslo, Stockholm, Copenhagen, Helsinki, and many more. Discover detailed information about parking rates and EV charging within our app.

With the Recharge app, you can effortlessly navigate to all of life's experiences across the entire Nordic region. Pay directly in the app or with a simple tap using Recharge's own charging card.
Charge your electric car at all Recharge charging stations throughout the Nordic region. With the new Recharge app, you can:
- Start and stop charging directly in the app.
- Get an overview of all Recharge chargers.
- Filter by charging speed, availability, and charging connectors.
- View charging history.
- Wirelessly charge easily with Recharge's own charging card.

Virta is a mobile service for charging your electric vehicle. Charge faster, easier & smarter. With Virta’s EV charging mobile service, you can view and adjust the charging event remotely. Charge with a same account at all Virta’s charging points – at home, work and on the move. Just plug in your car - we’ll do the rest. 

View a real-time map of the state of charging points (Available – Charging – Out of order)
Navigate to the location
Start and stop charging
Monitor charging remotely

In addition to our charging network, users can charge with Virta account all over Europe through our roaming partners! Our 24/7 help desk is available in several languages.

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

Ilmaiset ja huipputarkat kartat maastoon, vesille, retkeilyyn ja töihin. Mukana myös ilmaiset marja- ja sienikartat sekä retkeilykohteet. Syvyyskartat, merikartat, offline-kartat, jatkuvasti ajantasaiset vektorimuotoiset kiinteistötiedot sekä paljon lisää toimintoja Plus-tilauksella.

Maksuttomat toiminnot:
- Maanmittauslaitoksen tarkin ja ajantasaisin maastokartta
- Marjojen ja sienten kasvupaikat: Mustikka, puolukka, kantarelli, suppilovahvero, herkkutatti ja männynherkkutatti
- Retkeilyaineistot, kuten laavut, hiihtoladut ja moottorikelkkareitit, kymmeniä tuhansia kohteita
- Ilmakuva-aineistot koko Suomesta
- Kaupunki- ja taajamakartta, sisältää kadunnimet ja numerot
- Upea, retkeilykäyttöön erinomaisesti soveltuva Norjan maastokartta
- Syvyyskartta Perus - Maastokarttaan sisältyvät pienempien järvien syvyyskäyrät ja -lukemat. Kattavammat syvyystiedot Plus-tilauksella.
- Kiinteistökartta Perus - Kiinteistörajat ja -tunnukset, päivitetään väliajoin kiinteistörekisteristä. Plus-tilauksella jatkuvasti ajantasaiset kiinteistötiedot.
- Tarkka oma GPS-sijainti, sijainnin seuranta ja nopeusnäyttö. Edellyttää laitteessa olevaa GPS-vastaanotinta.
- Kartan kääntö kulkusuuntaan, kompassinäyttö sekä suuntaviiva ja etäisyys kohteeseen. Toiminto edellyttää laitteessa olevaa digitaalista kompassia.
- Omien paikkojen ja reittien tallennus, hallinta avainsanoilla sekä tuonti ja vienti GPX-muodossa
- Sijainnin avaaminen toisesta sovelluksesta (esim. geokätköilysovellukset)
- Maanmittauslaitoksen kanssa kehitetty karttapalautetoiminto, jolla voit ehdottaa karttoihin päivityksiä

Plus-tilauksella:
- Karttojen kätevä lataus offline-käyttöön
- Syvyyskartta Plus - Kattavimmat, maastokarttoihin lisätyt veneily- ja kalastuskäyttöön erinomaisesti soveltuvat syvyyskäyrät ja -lukemat perustuen Liikenneviraston merikarttatietokantaan. Katso tarkemmat tiedot sivulta www.karttaselain.fi/syvyystiedot
- Traficomin merikarttoihin perustuvat tarkimmat merikartta-aineistot (www.karttaselain.fi/merikartat)
- Karttojen kätevä lataus offline-käyttöön
- Ajantasainen vektorimuotoinen kiinteistökartta ja rajamerkit. Kiinteistöjen pinta-alat ja kiinteistöjen haku.
- Metsäortokuva havu- ja lehtipuuston erottamiseen sekä rinnevarjostekartta
- Paikkamerkkien ja reittien tallennus turvallisesti Karttaselain-tiliin
- Synkronoi paikat ja reitit automaattisesti web- ja mobiiliversioiden välillä
- Reitin suunnittelu ja piirretyn alueen pinta-alan määritys
- Reitin seuranta
- Kurssi ja kurssiviiva
- GPS-tarkkuuden näyttö
- Paikantimien seuranta, Koira-GPS ja henkilö- tai ajoneuvopaikannus (www.karttaselain.fi/paikantimet)
- Oma riista -metsästysalueiden lisäys ja selaaminen kartalla
- Kuljetun reitin pinta-alan määritys

Voit aktivoida 14 päivän maksuttoman kokeilujakson Plus-tilaukseen luomalla Karttaselain-tilin. Tämän jälkeen voit jatkaa Plus-toimintojen käyttöä ostamalla Plus-tilauksen (10,49 € / 2 kuukautta tai 40,49 € / 12 kuukautta) sovelluksen sisältä tai verkkokaupastamme (app.karttaselain.fi/buy). Tutustu myös usean käyttäjän Karttaselain tiimeille -tilaukseen sivulla www.karttaselain.fi/business. Lisää tietoa Karttaselaimesta sivustollamme www.karttaselain.fi.

Karttaselainta kehitetään yhdessä käyttäjäyhteisön kanssa! Tule mukaan keskusteluun vaikkapa Facebookissa, Instagramissa tai antamalla arvio App Storessa.

Asiantunteva asiakaspalvelumme palvelee osoitteessa www.karttaselain.fi/support

Huomaa, että jatkuva GPS:n käyttö saattaa selkeästi vähentää laitteesi toiminta-aikaa akkukäytössä.
---------------------------------------
English Description:
Karttaselain combines the high-quality topographic and nautical maps with exciting and up to date location based information. The POI (point of interest) information is collected from various sources and is updated all the time.

Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

Currently Karttaselain includes maps from Finland and Norway and is available in Finnish only.

Fortum Charge & Drive Finland: Charging your EV on the road 

With our service, you’ll enjoy a seamless charging experience and quick access to over 44,000 charging points across the Nordics. 

Connect effortlessly with Recharge,  IONITY, Lidl, Virta, K-Lataus, and many more — all through a single app and charging key.

WITH FORTUM CHARGE & DRIVE, YOU CAN:

• Get access to 5,7000 charging points across Finland and more than 44,000 across the Nordics.
• Easily start and stop charging with the charging key or the app.
• Locate charging stations near you or plan your journey with Route Planner.
• Filter chargers by type, speed, price and availability to find one that suits your needs.
• Tailor your search based on your vehicle compatibility.
• Set preferred operators or save your favorite charging points.
• Stay informed with real-time pricing.
• Add flexible payment options with debit/credit card, charging key or Google Pay or Apple Pay.
• Track your charging history in one place.

JOIN THE FORTUM CHARGE & DRIVE NETWORK AND EXPERIENCE STRESS-FREE EV CHARGING WITH OUR EXTENSIVE NETWORK.

Get Started Today: 
1. Download the Fortum Charge & Drive app for free. 
2. Quickly set up your account. 
3. Add a payment method or charging key/card (RFID tag) to prepare for your first charging session. 
4. Easily locate nearby public charging stations on the charging map or use Route Planner to plan your trip, and start your charging session with just a tap. 

EXPERIENCE THE CONVENIENCE OF PUBLIC EV CHARGING WITH FORTUM CHARGE & DRIVE

Designed to make your public charging easy and efficient, our app ensures you can find and use charging stations on the go. Whether you’re commuting, traveling, or running errands, Fortum Charge & Drive provides real-time information and seamless integration to enhance your charging experience. Enjoy the extensive charging network, effortless start and payment options, and the intelligent planning of your routes with our advanced Route Planner.

Lataa Autoliiton ilmainen Kansainvälisen ajokortin tilaussovellus puhelimeesi!
Sovelluksella voit täyttää Kansainvälisen ajokortin hakemuksen, ottaa hakemukseen kuvan, tilata
tarvitsemasi korttityypin sekä suorittaa maksun.

Autoliiton Kansainvälisen ajokortin tilaussovelluksella tilaat helposti kansainvälisen ajokortin kotiisi
puhelimellasi. Sovellus auttaa sinua valitsemaan oikean korttityypin matkustusmaasi perusteella.
Halutessasi voit tilata molemmat kortit. Ajokorttiin vaadittavan passikuvan voit ottaa sovelluksen avulla
suoraan puhelimella, tai valita halutun kuvan puhelimen muistista.

Île-de-France Mobilités is here to assist you daily. Purchase a digital ticket, recharge your Navigo pass, search for routes including trains, RERs, metros, trams, buses, coaches, bicycles, Vélib', car-sharing, or car rentals. Find schedules in real-time or traffic information... Discover essential tools and information for organizing your travels in Île-de-France. Together, let's travel with ease.

Avoid queues at stations: buy your transport tickets from your iPhone!
The following tickets are available for purchase:

- Metro-Train tickets or Bus-Tram Ticket
- One Way from/to Airports (you cannot purchase this ticket if you already have a Metro-Train Ticket charged on your device)
- Navigo daily (this fare doesn’t permit you to go to airports), weekly, or monthly passes
- Special fares (Anti-pollution pass, Paris-Visit Passes etc.)
- Daily Vélib’ passes

Purchased tickets can then be (depending on the chosen purchasing path):

- Stored on the iPhone and validated directly at stations (from iPhone Xr and iOS 17.5)
- Loaded onto your Navigo pass (from an iPhone 7, with at least iOS 13. iPhone XR and XS are compatible starting from iOS 14.5)

For compatible tickets (Metro-Train and Bus-Tram Tickets, Navigo Day passes, special fares), no account is needed, and you can pay directly with Apple Pay!

You can prepare and plan your travels:

- Find nearby bus stops, train stations, and metro stations
- Search for real-time public transport routes, car-sharing, and bicycle routes
- Save upcoming trips in your phone’s calendar
- Check the next departures for your lines in real-time and all the timetable information
- View maps of public transport networks (accessible even offline)
- Follow pedestrian routes for walking segment

Stay informed and anticipate disruptions:

- Check your lines’ Twitter feed for real-time traffic updates
- Get alerts for disruptions on your favorite lines and routes
- Stay updated on the status of elevators in the stations you use

Customize your travel:

- Save your destinations (work, home, gym, etc.), stations, and stops as favorites
- Customize your profile (fast walker, with difficulties, reduced mobility, etc.)
- Select lines or stations to avoid

Prefer soft or alternative modes of transport:

- Book car-sharing and/or ride-sharing trips in partnership with leading providers
- Opt for bicycle routes for all your trips
- Rent a car or a van for a short period by choosing a Communauto car-sharing vehicle from a wide selection of stations around you and book it immediately for the duration of your choice.
--
Already using the Île-de-France Mobilités app and enjoying its services? Let us know with a 5-star rating!
Experiencing bugs or having feedback to give? Help us improve by sending your suggestions through the contact form available via the personal space.
Sähköautoilijat ry:n ylläpitämästä latauspistekartasta löydät sähköautollesi sopivat latauspisteet (keskinopeat sekä pikalatauspisteet) sekä tarkempia tietoja ja valokuvia niiden sijaintipaikasta.

Moovit is one app for all your urban mobility and transport rides!

Dailymail - "This travel app is a godsend for anyone using public transport – with live updates to bus schedules, as well as a great route-planner for cities across the UK."

Transportation is an integral part of urban living. Whether you ride the train, subway/underground /tube, bus, light rail, ferry or metro, use bikes, ride-sharing like Uber, getting the best urban mobility information is critical. Moovit guides you from point A to B in the easiest and most efficient way. Get train and bus times, maps, and live arrival times with ease so you can plan your trip with confidence. Find critical alerts and service disruptions for your favorite lines. Get step-by-step directions of optimal route bus, train, metro, bike or a combination of them. 
This is why Moovit has been named one of the best apps of the year 2017 by the App Store!

Moovit guides more than 865 million users in over 3200 cities throughout the world.

► Journey Planner that combines you all transport options and gives you the best route with live arrivals.

► Live Directions: Get step-by-step directions with live guidance as you travel: know exactly how long you need to walk to your station, how long you’re waiting, view the arrival time of your line and how many stops are left. 

► Real time arrivals. View real-time arrival updates, which are taken directly from GPS devices positioned on buses and trains.

► Real time alerts. Know about issues ahead of time by receiving service alerts such as emergency or unexpected disruptions, delays, traffic jams, new construction and more...

► Users reports. Moovit’s users report issues found with stations, line service, and timetables so that we can inform all nearby riders about what’s going on in their area.

► Favorite lines, stations, and places. Get easy access to lines, stations, and places you ride and visit all the time. Plus, get real-time updates if/when there are changes to your favorite lines in case your bus or train time is impacted!

► Bike routes. Get bike routes in addition to the bus, subway, train, or metro trip plans. If you ride bikes (yours or shared) we can plan a route that includes the train or bus. 
Bike docking stations are updated in real-time.

► Maps view. View all stations, routes, and lines on the subway or bus map. Additionally, maps are available in PDF for when you’re offline, or underground on the subway. 

Ride with Moovit in all major cities:

UK:
• London
• Manchester
• Birmingham
• Leeds
• Edinburgh
• Glasgow
• Liverpool
• Sheffield

Ireland:
• Dublin and all of the Republic of Ireland. 

Moovit supports all major transit:

UK:
• TFL - Bus, Tube, DLR, Overground, Ferry (River Bus), Tfl Rail, Tram, Coach
• National Express
• National Rail
• Arriva
• First
• Stagecoach and more...

Ireland:
• Bus Eireann
• Dublin Bus
• Irish Rail
• Luas
• Kenneally’s Bus Service and more…

Bike sharing provided by:
• Santander Cycles in London
• BelfastBikes in Belfast
• Bike in Bath

India:
•Delhi: Delhi Metro (DMRC), Delhi Buses (DTC), Northern Railways (NR)
•Mumbai: Mumbai Metro (M.M.R.D.A), all buses: BEST, NMMT, KDMT, VVMT, MBMT, KMT, TMT, Ferries and more
•Bangalore: Namma Metro, B.M.T.C (buses and metro feeder routes), South Western Railways
•Chennai: Chennai Metro Rail, all buses - Metropolitan Transport Corporation (MTA)
•Ahmedabad: A.M.T.S, Bus Rapid Transport System (BRTS), V.T.C.O.S 
•Pune: Indian Railways, Pune Local Central Railways, Pune Mahanagar Parivahan Mahaman.

Singapore:
• MRT, LRT, bus, tram, cable car & shuttle buses. Service provided by:
• SBS
• SMRT
• Tower Transit
• Go-Ahead Singapore

You ride, we guide!

Feel free to contact us:

https://moovitapp.zendesk.com/hc/requests/new
moovit@Facebook, Twitter

Terms of Use
https://moovitapp.com/en-us/legal/terms-of-service-en

Travel confidently around London with Transport for London's official app, built around our iconic live Tube map. Try switching to step-free mode and watch the map adjust to show only accessible stations, ensuring your journeys are as smooth as possible. With a clear, user-friendly design, TfL Go is easy for everyone to use.

Find the Best Route
We'll suggest multiple ways to get to your destination, whether by Tube, London Overground, Elizabeth line, DLR, Tram, National Rail, IFS Cloud Cable Car, or even cycling and walking. You choose the route that suits you best.

Check Before You Travel
Get live arrival times for Buses, Tube, London Overground, Elizabeth Line, DLR, Tram, and National Rail. Check the live status of all TfL lines and stations directly on the map, or view a summary of current disruptions in the "Status" section.

Freedom to Explore
Find travel options tailored to your needs, including step-free journeys and routes avoiding stairs or escalators. Journey plans automatically adapt to the accessibility status of stations, helping you avoid disruptions. TfL Go also supports VoiceOver and Dynamic Type, making it more accessible for everyone.

Manage Your Payments
Create an account or log in to manage your payments for travel across London. Top up pay as you go credit or purchase Travelcards for your Oyster card, and view your journey history for both Oyster and contactless cards registered to your account.

Note: Oyster and contactless accounts can only be accessed within UK/Europe.

Understand Station Facilities
Check how busy a station is right now, or see if it has toilets or Wi-Fi access. Find detailed information about step-free access and interchanges including platform gap width, step height and boarding methods available.

What People Are Saying:
"...a surprisingly phenomenal app for commuters travelling via public transport in London!"
"One of the finest transport apps there is, well thought out, well designed and well executed."
"The most accurate app in London for bus times"
"Fantastic app if only just to have a live Tube map / bus tracker in your pocket at all times!"
"TfL Go is your number one stop for live tube and bus arrivals"

Get in Touch
Any questions, feedback or something we've missed? Email us at tflappfeedback@tfl.gov.uk

Bonjour RATP is the essential app for all your journeys in Île-de-France.
Plan your trips, check live traffic, purchase your tickets, and discover all mobility alternatives around you - metro, RER, bus, tram, Transilien trains, and self-service bikes.

Your routes across all networks.
Metro, RER, bus, tramway, Transilien SNCF trains, Optile… Wherever you are, Bonjour RATP finds the best journey to get you around the entire region.

Journeys tailored to you. 
Customize your search according to your preferences:
- Avoid certain lines or stations,
- Prioritize your preferred modes (metro, RER, Transilien, bus…),
- Minimize transfers or favor accessible routes.
Because every resident of Île-de-France has their own way of traveling.

Real-time traffic and personalized alerts.
Check the network status at a glance and receive real-time alerts in case of disruptions on your favorite lines across the entire Île-de-France network.

All your tickets in your pocket. 
No more monthly queues! Buy the following tickets in the app and access them directly on your iPhone or Navigo pass:
- Navigo Month
- Navigo Week
- Navigo Day
- Metro-Train-RER tickets
- Bus-Tram tickets
- Paris Region-Airports tickets
- Special tickets (Music Festival, Anti-pollution pass...)
- Paris Visite pass

Always on time.
Check real-time schedules for upcoming departures on all your lines. Never miss your bus, metro, or RER again. An incident on your lines? Thanks to alerts, you’ll be immediately informed and the app will suggest an alternative.

Speak and go (Beta)
Just say where you want to go, and Bonjour RATP takes care of the rest!
Voice search makes your journeys even easier.

Bike sharing
Want to ride? Find a bike in seconds. Bonjour RATP shows availability of Vélib’, Lime, and Dott.

Why choose Bonjour RATP?
- Complete coverage across all Île-de-France
- Customizable routes based on your preferences and habits
- Real-time traffic and alerts
- All tickets and passes directly in the app
- All self-service bikes available
- Smooth, clear, and intuitive interface

For more information about our services, feel free to contact us by email at clients@bonjour-ratp.fr

Lataa SEONappi ja suosi suomalaisen, paikallisen, yrittäjävetoisen sekä uusiutuvan polttoaineiden jakeluketjun palveluita!

Kirjautumalla sovellukseen saat kännykkääsi kattavat SEO:n palvelut.

SEONapilla voi tilata kätevästi polttoöljyä lämmitykseen ja moottorikäyttöön. Ensimmäisen tilauskerran jälkeen polttoöljyn tilaushistoria tallentuu appiin, jonka jälkeen ”uusi aiempi tilaus”
-toiminto tulee käyttöön.

Matkareitin suunnittelu on SEONapilla sujuvaa ja lähimmät SEO-asemat voi hakea palveluittain. Asemista voi valita omat suosikkinsa, jolloin asemien tarjoamia palveluita ja etuja on helppoa seurata. SEONapissa saat rahanarvoisia etuja ketjutasolla ja kauppiasvetoisilla asemillamme.

SEONapin ominaisuuksia:

Sovelluksella polttoöljyn tilaaminen on helppoa ja nopeaa. Sovelluksen käyttäjille oma, halvempi hinta. Tilaushistoria löytyy jatkossa omasta kännykästä, jolloin uuden tilauksen tekeminen on helppoa.

Suunnittele matkareittisi ja löydä lähimmät SEO-asemasi. Asemaverkostostamme voit etsiä asemia palveluiden perusteella.

Valitse omat suosikki asemasi ja jatkossa löydät helposti näiden asemien palvelutarjoaman, lounaslistat ja asemakohtaiset edut.

Tarjoamme rahanarvoisia etuja paikallisesti.

Full-featured digital GPS speedometer.

√ Trip computer for current speed, max speed, avg speed, distance, travel time, stop time
√ Measure acceleration from 0 to 60 mph and more
√ Speed limit warning with HUDWAY mode

Notice: Using location services extensively may affect battery power consumption.

Tracker app is the best on the market live tracking and navigation app for outdoor enthusiasts whether you are hiking or hunting.

FREE VERSION 
Tracker app is the best free app on the market for outdoor navigation. With the free version you can track your own position on a terrain or a satellite map and utilize the advanced Safety feature, where your location is seen anonymously on the map by other nearby nature movers and you can also see them when the feature in use. In addition, you can add and save markings on the map of your outdoor adventures. By updating to the full version you will get access to all features: to track your dogs and friends, use advanced group functions and additional map materials. Advanced Dog Safety and Wolf Safety functions are available in the full version. 

FULL VERSION 
With the full verion of the app you easily keep track of both your own and your dog’s position in real time on high-quality maps. In addition the realtime locations of your group members are visible on your map. The app allows you to set waypoints and lines on the map and communicate and share the info with your friends within the group. 
The Tracker app also works as a safety aid as it uses advanced Safety features. You can see anonymously on the map nearby persons using the app and in the full version also dogs when the Dog Safety feature is in use. Wolf observations made by other users are visible on the map thanks to Wolf Safety.  

RELIABLE POSITIONING ON HIGH-QUALITY MAPS 
In the full version of the Tracker app you can easily locate your group members, track and trace your dog in real time from your own mobile device. The app offers an excellent selection of up-to-date terrain maps  as well as satellite maps for seamless navigation. It includes high quality maps from Finland, Sweden, Norway, Germany, France, Austria, Switzerland, Czech Republic and Estonia. In addition it includes good quality maps in all other countries globally. The app includes versatile tools to make quick and easy map markings, draw areas, measure distances, add markers and pins, create map collections, add external map layers and share them with friends and your hunting group. 
 
GROUP FUNCTIONS 
Tracker app increases your chances of successful outdoor adventure e.g. in a hunting group. You can effectively communicate and collaborate with your friends, with the hunting group and make decisions based on reliable information. It is very easy to create groups based on your needs, invite friends to join the group with an invitation link, add dogs to a group, share map markings with the group and much more. All group members always have real time information on locations of other group members, dog tracks, targets, and map markers.  
 
SAFETY 
Safety function enhances security during hiking or hunting by showing anonymously on the map all the other nature movers outside of your group who has Tracker or Ultracom app in use and are in the same area. The Tracker app also works as a safety aid with advanced Safety features where you can see anonymously on the map other nearby persons, dogs and also wolf alerts made by other users.

About IONITY
IONITY builds and operates Europe’s largest ultra-fast charging network. With a High-Power Charging (HPC) capacity of up to 400 kW, it enables maximum charging speeds. IONITY exclusively uses renewable energy, ensuring emission-free and carbon-neutral driving. Currently, the IONITY network includes over 700 charging stations and more than 4,800 HPC charging points across 24 European countries.

IONITY was founded in 2017 and is a joint venture between the car manufacturers BMW Group, Ford Motor Company, Hyundai Motor Group, Kia, Mercedes-Benz AG and Volkswagen Group with Audi and Porsche as well as BlackRock's Climate Infrastructure Platform as a financial investor. The company is headquartered in Munich, Germany, and has additional offices in Dortmund, Germany, the French metropolis Paris, and outside the Norwegian capital Oslo.
